{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464800/extras/\u6807\u98981-\u82f1\u6587.png?t=1711198527\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464800/extras/\u63cf\u8ff0\u533aGif.gif?t=1711198527\" /><br>Enjoy limitless dodging, infinite sprinting, zero cooldowns on abilities, and instant enemy eliminations. Controls are user-friendly, making it easy for beginners. Yet, higher levels demand skilled tactics and strategies.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464800/extras/\u6807\u98982-\u82f1\u6587.png?t=1711198527\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464800/extras/\u89d2\u8272\u64cd\u4f5c2.png?t=1711198527\" /><br>Initially, you'll control just one heroine. But as you advance to the game's second phase, you'll gain the freedom to choose from six unique characters at no extra cost. Each character boasts distinctive traits and entirely different combat styles, offering a fresh gameplay experience.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464800/extras/\u6807\u98983-\u82f1\u6587.png?t=1711198527\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464800/extras/\u6b66\u5668.png?t=1711198527\" /><br>Your main heroine can wield five different types of weapons, each offering a unique combat style and feel. Throughout the game, you'll encounter weapon-switching stations where you can change your weapon for free. If you find yourself struggling, a simple weapon swap could turn the tide of battle.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464800/extras/\u6807\u98984-\u82f1\u6587.png?t=1711198527\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464800/extras/\u5173\u5361.png?t=1711198527\" /><br>Face off against dozens of enemies and bosses, each with their own unique combat mechanics, making every level a rich and varied challenge. Some levels demand high levels of skill, while others require strategic thinking. But no matter the challenge, you'll always find a way to triumph\u2014it's all up to you!<br><br><strong>In the Ghost Zone Where Humans Dare Not Tread</strong><br>Signals of metahuman activity have been detected. You'll step into the shoes of a rookie member of the Metahuman Watch, joining forces with five teammates to venture into this enigmatic realm. Your mission? To fight fire with fire and unravel the dark secrets lurking behind the scenes.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Welcome to Apex Heroines!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2464800/bc09c571119c829534329ceed0d924fe3800d79c.jpg"},{"name":"Initial Mission","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2464800/05d7b9005cc5bdbb5bd1fff51702ca1d88d55c4c.jpg"},{"name":"Rescue Akane","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2464800/b8fa19b48cba03896a9d59a094b71f58598f3d70.jpg"},{"name":"Rescue Midori","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2464800/88c9138a541582444e4cbcb2e1ce8587827348de.jpg"},{"name":"Rescue Rosalind","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2464800/f665777f6b9d5251a05c18ec0d7dfa18bcf810f7.jpg"},{"name":"Rescue Kamui","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2464800/0e8df753d967a70043561d7c20fc88ea77e36927.jpg"},{"name":"Rescue Lighting","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2464800/99bca1e7bc227cc730255427c39394b0b4bb40bf.jpg"},{"name":"Monster-Type\uff1aMedusa","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommuni